HEADWORD: xi
<hw>xi</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adj.</pos> <def>The Roman number
symbolizing the value eleven. Used after a noun it may symbolize the
ordinal number; <as>as, Superbowl <ex>XI</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> eleven, 11.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Xian</ent>⟦br⟧
